article_title: Out-of-state interests seek to influence Tennessee's legislators

article_metadata.description: NASHVILLE -- Out-of-state interests have long sought to shape public policy in Tennessee, but some national organizations that are relative newcomers to the Volunteer State have added millions of dollars to the mix of political money and lobbying intended to achieve that influence.
